				<a href="http://foreclosureattorneyboston.com/best-tips-for-choosing-a-foreclosure-attorney/" title="Permalink to Best tips for choosing a foreclosure attorney" rel="bookmark">Best tips for choosing a foreclosure attorney</a>
			</h1>
